==Description==
The pride of the local Teladi sectors is this colony; the high tower of the Ministry of Finance stands high on the planet's surface. The Ministry was set up to oversee the Compagny's finances when setting up new sectors, although this wing of the Teladi Compagny wasn't entirely successful. When the neighbouring system, [[Bad Debt]], was first opened to the public, the sector ran into troubleand the Ministry was held responsible. The colony skyline is dominated by the 80 story tower that casts a shadow over the gardens of trade, a large garden filled with markets and made more appealing to visiting [[Argon]] and [[Boron]] traders.

